---
title: Smart Panko Pork Chops with Creamy Yogurt Dressing
description: This Smart meal packs a real flavour punch! Juicy panko-crusted pork chops are the perfect topper for a veggie-filled salad, drizzled in DIY herby lemon-yogurt dressing to balance out the plate.

